track_notes: Park tidily opposite the entrance to the fish farm. Walk up the track until you pass over the second main stream coming down and head straight up for the highest point you can see.  When it levels out there is a short walk to the true summit.  Steep and not very pleasant but quick!
track_title: From fish farm at Moll - direct route

track_notes: Park tidily opposite the fish farm entrance.  Follow the track until it ends and then head straight up hill (lots of holes and bogs) until you get out of the area dug out for forestry.  Turn half right and follow up heathery/grassy slopes to the summit. Longer than the direct route, but a bit easier on the legs.
track_title: From fish farm at Moll - less steep route
